      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean \"very strong\" sounds like it might just mean i'll sleep really deeply lol. i've had wine before and it helps me relax, so i figured it would just complement the medicine. if it's just one glass, is there actually any real danger to it or is it just a bit more sleepy than usual?",
