      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"More sleepy\" is an understatement; you are asking to stack two central nervous system depressants, which is a medical no-no. While a small glass might just make you *too* sleepy, the real danger is respiratory depression, which is when your breathing slows down dangerously. For guaranteed, safe sleep, stick strictly to the dosage your doctor prescribed and avoid any alcohol entirely.",
      "source": "target",
